ith the help of\nvarious concrete and relevant examples, such as the unit sphere and the\nPoincar\\'{e} half plane.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 29 Dec 2015 12:47:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 31 Dec 2015 11:18:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-01-01"}
