. Numerical simulations illustrate the\ninefficiency of the Nash equilibrium outcome and motivate further research on\ncooperative or coordinated schemes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 29 Dec 2015 13:41:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-12-31"}
